      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is the perfect candidate for your next big project. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and some TLC to the body and interior, it offers a fantastic foundation for someone looking to bring a classic back to life. It's priced to sell and ready for a dedicated owner to give it the attention it deserves!",
