    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and some fading in the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and a small tear in the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and the AC are still functioning properly. Mechanically, the car starts and runs fine, but it will likely need new brake pads and a suspension tune-up in the near future as there is some minor rattling over bumps. It's a solid, functional car that has been used regularly and is priced to reflect its honest, well-loved state.",
